data.message:
TEST123
The only supported versions are 1.18.2 and 1.19.2.
Any other version is ***__NOT__*** supported.
${name-data.name} is ***__NOT__*** supported.
You can search the <#${name-data.support-channel}> and <#${name-data.bug-channel}> channels to try to find a solution to your problem.

It is virtually impossible to maintain a large amount of different versions concurrently and still provide new content, and to provide support for older versions that aren't maintained anymore. Please respect the devs' decision.
If you insistently ask about any other version than 1.18.2 and 1.19.2, moderation action will be taken.
